s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2FIN1702270059.htm&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4b3e59f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2017/02/27/IN1702270059.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年 6月<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會請願促延長侍產假及產假　料對企業經營影響很小</span></strong><br />\n工聯會一批代表到政府總部門請願，要求政府盡快將男士侍產假增加到7日<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402048-20180616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402048-20180616.htm&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f79ef3e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402048-20180616.htm&h=b4e24868\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402048-20180616.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6381be0533fc69ec64638c3df57927fd50cd2a65","tid":874642,"uid":205844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"支持工聯會推生仔冇產假放，係公司個位到生完剪埋臍帶好即刻埋位做野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d2f960b4a5302695b0f403428635ec653ad34e","tid":874642,"uid":30647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2017/02/28/a11b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2Fa11b.jpg&h=11ba83a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20120617/photo/0617-00407-031b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120617%2Fphoto%2F0617-00407-031b1.jpg&h=6da494ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2016/05/04/d/d2dde76416e0dfeb8db45c266d8acd0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2016%2F05%2F04%2Fd%2Fd2dde76416e0dfeb8db45c266d8acd0f.jpg&h=4c15a838&s={SIZE}\" />"